    dc:title "Note on the presence of Hystrix (Mammalia, Rodentia) in the Malawi Chiwondo Beds (Plio-Pleistocene): taphonomical and palaeoecological implications" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597172>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4608731> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4597172>
    dc:description "FIG. 1. — Fossil and modern Hystrix Linnaeus, 1758 specimens: A, Hystrix sp. upper left M3 Uraha (HCRP-1144); B, Hystrix makap­ anensis Greenwood, 1958 upper left M3 from Upper Laetolil Beds, Laetoli (EP3354/00- Loc.15); C, modern H. cristata Linnaeus, 1758 from Senegal (MNHN-CG1995-3133) juvenile with upper right M2 and M3 just erupted; D, modern H. cristata (MNHN-CG1962-2223) worn upper left M23. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4597172/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4608731>
    dc:description "FIG. 2. — Scatter plot of the length versus width of the modern and fossil Hystrix M3 (after data in Table 1)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4608731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

